OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThe rest of the night will be mainly
OL,8,Fdry with variable amounts of cloud and
OL,9,Fjust the odd passing shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA mainly dry day with
OL,12,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells, though the odd
OL,14,Fshower is possible. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry
OL,17,Fwith some sunny spells on Sunday and
OL,18,FMonday. Rain spreading east on
OL,19,FTuesday, drier later.
